    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at MRL 5 for all factors. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification with N=2000 samples confirms 95% prediction intervals on hemolysis index remain below the absolute clinical threshold across all five operating points. Validation activities directly cover the COU geometry, fluid, and operating range. The credibility evidence package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for this Class III VAD device.",
